item.description: Actor Jonathan Bailey sits down with Michelle Miller to discuss his on-screen romance roles in both "Bridgerton" and "Fellow Travelers." Then, Seth Doane travels to the Italian coastal town of Polignano a Mare to meet the athletes who compete in the thrilling sport of cliff diving. "Here Comes the Sun" is a closer look at some of the people, places and things we bring you every week on "CBS Sunday Morning."
